text: Anzhela Temirova (; born 24 May 1987) is an Azerbaijani former footballer who played as a goalkeeper. She has been a member of the Azerbaijan women's national team. ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football goalkeepers Category:Azerbaijani women's footballers Category:Azerbaijan women's international footballers
